10.11.21.136,<*> "GET /openstack/<* HTTP/1.1" status: 200 len: 124 time: <*


### Solution:
```python
def parse_log(log):
    template = ''
    log = log.split()
    for word in log:
        if word.isnumeric():
            template += '<*>'
        elif word == 'HTTP/1.1':
            template += '<*>'
        else:
            template += word +''
    return template.strip()
```

